1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:07,980
[The Eternal Fragrance]
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 2]

4
00:01:20,670 --> 00:01:21,340
Who's there?

5
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,170
It's you...

6
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,010
It's you!

7
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,580
You followed me again!

8
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,220
Followed you?

9
00:01:52,830 --> 00:01:54,730
I have no money for an inn, so I can only stay here.

10
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,940
I was here first anyway.

11
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:01,940
When did you get here? What did you hear?

12
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,650
I slept

13
00:02:05,270 --> 00:02:08,060
until the aroma of roast chicken woke me.

14
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:20,650
Sir,

15
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:23,900
have we met somewhere before?

16
00:02:28,390 --> 00:02:30,900
I'm Lei Xiuyuan, an exam applicant.

17
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:34,180
I think we've never met.

18
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,940
We're here for the exam too.

19
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:41,250
Fate brought us together. Let's journey together

20
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,940
and look out for each other.

21
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,410
- Great idea... - No way!

22
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:51,090
Who are you? What's your motive?

23
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,570
Speak properly, Xiaobangchui.

24
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:53,250
Quiet!

25
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:56,300
First Shanhua, then the academy exam.

26
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,220
As if I'd believe you. Speak!

27
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:08,220
Chufeng Academy is the safest place in the world.

28
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:11,970
It remains neutral through immortal feuds

29
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,370
and mortal wars alike.

30
00:03:14,990 --> 00:03:15,940
Shanhua is in danger.

31
00:03:17,670 --> 00:03:20,850
Only by getting into the academy can I save him.

32
00:03:27,390 --> 00:03:29,180
You said your master's lost.

33
00:03:29,390 --> 00:03:30,850
Why take the academy exam suddenly?

34
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,370
I…?

35
00:03:32,870 --> 00:03:34,650
I need to improve my skills to find my master.

36
00:03:35,830 --> 00:03:36,530
Me too.

37
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,220
Only strength

38
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:39,900
can protect the ones I love.

39
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,370
Why keep staring at me?

40
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:13,090
I'm not that tomboy.

41
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,370
Xigu Village lies in Gaolu.

42
00:04:22,790 --> 00:04:23,890
Since you're from Gaolu,

43
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,770
do you know Mr. Lei, the military commander?

44
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:37,810
Gaolu Kingdom is long gone.

45
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:41,250
I have no country, no home left.

46
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:42,770
No country, no home…

47
00:04:43,790 --> 00:04:44,570
I'm just like you,

48
00:04:45,590 --> 00:04:47,100
homeless and stateless.

49
00:04:51,710 --> 00:04:54,060
Your clothes are torn. My sister can sew.

50
00:04:54,470 --> 00:04:55,740
Let her mend them for you.

51
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:57,810
No need.

52
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,540
We have trials tomorrow. Better look decent.

53
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:15,740
Your Highness.

54
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,090
[Young Ye Ye]

55
00:05:16,090 --> 00:05:17,300
Hurry, take off your robe and give it to him.

56
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:20,100
Yuan, Mr. Lei died defending our realm.

57
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,420
As his adopted son,

58
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:24,210
you must safeguard His Highness like him.

59
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:25,500
Do you understand?

60
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,890
Are you truly unfamiliar with Mr. Lei?

61
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:41,890
I'll say this one last time: I do not know him.

62
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:43,420
Forget the torn clothes.

63
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,500
Hurry undress and get some sleep.

64
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:45,660
Don't you remember why we came to Lugong Town?

65
00:05:55,710 --> 00:05:56,450
My apologies.

66
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,770
I must've missed my old friend so much

67
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,210
that I mistook you for him.

68
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,890
[Lugong Town]
The spirit root test begins.

69
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:50,210
Fire Spirit Root. Pass.

70
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,420
You're amazing!

71
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,500
You'll definitely rank first.

72
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:02,180
What's a single Fire Spirit Root?

73
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:05,940
Spirit roots correspond to the Five Elements: Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, Earth.

74
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,420
Most folks have mixed spirit roots,

75
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,010
two or three kinds combined.

76
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,860
Only those with extraordinary talent

77
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,690
possess a single spirit root.

78
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:14,980
Anyone with a single spirit root

79
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,100
is a rare cultivation prodigy.

80
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,570
Single Wood Spirit Root.

81
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,060
Let's go.

82
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:29,740
Excuse me.

83
00:07:36,590 --> 00:07:37,450
Illusion talisman cheating!

84
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,660
Kick him out and blacklist him for life.

85
00:09:15,710 --> 00:09:17,300
Top Metal Spirit Root.

86
00:09:25,350 --> 00:09:26,090
Metal Spirit Root.

87
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:27,660
Pass.

88
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:32,540
Wait a minute.

89
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:37,140
Could it be another illusion talisman trick?

90
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,690
Lei Yuan, it's really you.

91
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,850
All those born with a Metal Spirit Root

92
00:09:55,230 --> 00:09:57,380
are destined for extraordinary immortal cultivation.

93
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:00,850
Come study under me.

94
00:10:01,110 --> 00:10:02,690
I will pass down all my knowledge without reserve.

95
00:10:03,870 --> 00:10:04,490
No need.

96
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:17,380
What's a Metal Spirit Root?

97
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,330
I don't think he can be better than you.

98
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:21,330
That old man must be senile.

99
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,420
There is always someone stronger.

100
00:10:24,830 --> 00:10:27,090
We should treat gifted folks with courtesy

101
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:28,490
and recruit them early.

102
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:34,690
Your Metal Spirit Root sounds so powerful.

103
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:36,210
Lend me some of it.

104
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:42,020
Spirit roots cannot be lent to others.

105
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,060
I…

106
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:00,730
- Your turn. - I…

107
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:02,690
She's calling you.

108
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:27,730
No spirit root detected.

109
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,020
Please check again.

110
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,260
Check more closely.

111
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:34,450
She truly has no spirit root at all.

112
00:11:36,990 --> 00:11:38,780
Please check more closely!

113
00:11:39,350 --> 00:11:41,690
Maybe my spirit root is hiding somewhere!

114
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:42,610
Please.

115
00:11:42,990 --> 00:11:43,780
Check again.

116
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:47,850
Xiaobangchui, hold your breath!

117
00:12:06,830 --> 00:12:08,450
W-What's that?

118
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:24,540
Dual weak spirit roots with Wood primary, and Earth secondary.

119
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:28,380
Pass.

120
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:32,420
Thanks.

121
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:43,330
Your meridians are sealed. No spirit roots can be detected.

122
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:46,540
Passed.

123
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,420
Clearly, it's a fox spirit's doing.

124
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,210
Riyan lives inside her.

125
00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:08,420
Lei.

126
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,420
What's up?

127
00:13:15,710 --> 00:13:17,060
Metal Spirit Roots are incredibly rare.

128
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:20,060
May I see yours again?

129
00:13:21,230 --> 00:13:21,850
No time.

130
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,850
Wait!

131
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:39,450
We can team up

132
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:40,660
for tomorrow's trial

133
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:41,900
to get into the academy faster.

134
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:43,300
I don't care about the academy.

135
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:47,020
Then why sit the exam?

136
00:13:48,680 --> 00:13:49,900
Who exactly are you?

137
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,490
Spirit or ghost,

138
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:57,420
come out now!

139
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:58,940
Or

140
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,540
I'll shave all my hair off,

141
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,450
so you'll have nowhere to hide.

142
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:04,690
Wait.

143
00:14:07,750 --> 00:14:08,730
Are you really a girl?

144
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,140
You'd sacrifice your own hair.

145
00:14:12,710 --> 00:14:14,490
You're that Qingqiu fox.

146
00:14:14,870 --> 00:14:15,680
[Riyan, Nine-Tailed Fox]

147
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:17,730
I'm a Nine-Tailed Fox with a thousand years of cultivation.

148
00:14:18,110 --> 00:14:19,090
My name is Riyan.

149
00:14:19,710 --> 00:14:21,020
Ri as in sunlight,

150
00:14:21,230 --> 00:14:22,810
Yan as in blazing flame.

151
00:14:23,470 --> 00:14:25,690
Riyan.

152
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:29,660
A thousand years of cultivation? Sounds powerful.

153
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:30,900
Why'd you hide inside me?

154
00:14:31,350 --> 00:14:32,490
Only because your ma...

155
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,900
I mean, you're such an unlucky fool.

156
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:37,210
I'm willing to aid you. Show some gratitude!

157
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:39,300
Come on! They were chasing you,

158
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,330
and you hid on my head!

159
00:14:43,230 --> 00:14:43,730
Wait!

160
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:47,020
You saw everything when I went

161
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:48,690
to the latrine and bathed!

162
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:52,180
My spirit body's injured, and all my senses shut down.

163
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:52,810
Besides,

164
00:14:53,830 --> 00:14:54,810
what's there to see anyway?

165
00:15:00,110 --> 00:15:03,690
Your spirit body's hurt? Is it that bad?

166
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:04,570
It's nothing much.

167
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:06,940
Might take three to five years to heal fully.

168
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,730
Three to five years? That's ages!

169
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,330
Will you pay rent for hiding here?

170
00:15:13,350 --> 00:15:14,420
Ignorant girl!

171
00:15:15,110 --> 00:15:16,540
I've condescended

172
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:18,060
to rest in your hair.

173
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:19,780
This is an honor for you!

174
00:15:21,830 --> 00:15:23,210
Old spirit,

175
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,020
you've grown shameless with age!

176
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:26,940
So it's you.

177
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:29,210
How many lovers have you ruined for centuries?

178
00:15:29,350 --> 00:15:30,210
What do you mean?

179
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:32,730
[Little Matchmaker]
I match people up and build goodwill.

180
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,940
You two know each other?

181
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:37,450
When you live long enough,

182
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:39,940
you're bound to meet shady folks.

183
00:15:40,710 --> 00:15:42,140
Right, stinky fox?

184
00:15:43,590 --> 00:15:44,570
He is here.

185
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:45,380
Xiaobangchui,

186
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:47,450
who are you talking to?

187
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:48,940
No one at all!

188
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,090
Come, I need to talk to you.

189
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:55,210
Really?

190
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:05,340
[Lugong Town]

191
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:25,040
[Yange Hall]

192
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:27,900
Thanks.

193
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,330
Don't just stare.

194
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:39,490
Here,

195
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:41,260
have some meat.

196
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,210
Trying to test me?

197
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:13,250
Here. Drink some water to cut the grease.

198
00:17:18,440 --> 00:17:19,180
Drink with me.

199
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,420
Still plotting against me.

200
00:17:35,230 --> 00:17:36,340
The truth-telling spell doesn't work.

201
00:17:52,230 --> 00:17:53,250
You poisoned the water too.

202
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,970
Your head's spinning, right?

203
00:17:58,790 --> 00:18:00,140
You took my soul-bewitching powder,

204
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:02,530
so your head is buzzing,

205
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:03,660
and your tongue won't cooperate, huh?

206
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:05,290
Yeah.

207
00:18:09,310 --> 00:18:11,690
Good. Tell me.

208
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:13,380
Why are you getting close to me?

209
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:23,290
Stop struggling. Tell the truth.

210
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,180
After my money?

211
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:27,940
Or my master?

212
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:31,010
Who's your master?

213
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,340
Not after my master.

214
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:34,900
Then what?

215
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:38,010
I... I need to survive

216
00:18:38,990 --> 00:18:39,820
to save Shanhua.

217
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:42,770
Save Shanhua? None of my business.

218
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:50,210
Won't talk, huh?

219
00:18:52,070 --> 00:18:53,140
Then meet your end.

220
00:18:54,510 --> 00:18:55,140
Sirs,

221
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:57,940
pay the bill before fighting, and take it outside.

222
00:18:58,360 --> 00:19:00,900
Otherwise, you can't afford

223
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:03,100
to break all these teapots and cups.

224
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,290
Thirty liang for this tea?

225
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:07,050
You're robbing us!

226
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:12,210
Can we... put it on credit?

227
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:16,530
Sorry, no credit here.

228
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:20,400
[Mr. Yan, Owner of Yange Hall]

229
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,580
He's a natural opera performer!

230
00:19:33,790 --> 00:19:35,250
Truly outstanding.

231
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:40,100
And he's got quite a temper.

232
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:43,860
I like that.

233
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,690
Mr. Yan. If you like him,

234
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:51,140
I'll sell him to you. Interested?

235
00:19:53,840 --> 00:19:55,450
He masters both literary and martial arts,

236
00:19:55,710 --> 00:19:58,250
the finest talent in Lugong Town.

237
00:19:58,960 --> 00:19:59,730
The price is merely a meal,

238
00:20:00,360 --> 00:20:02,940
plus leaked trial questions. What a bargain!

239
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:22,450
Why hasn't Xiuyuan come back yet?

240
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:26,180
He has a single spirit root.

241
00:20:26,470 --> 00:20:28,580
Some mentor might have recruited him

242
00:20:28,710 --> 00:20:29,530
on the spot.

243
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:33,380
You'd better worry about yourself.

244
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:35,940
This trial is said to be tougher than the previous ones.

245
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,580
By rough reckoning,

246
00:20:38,310 --> 00:20:41,010
less than ten percent will pass.

247
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:48,210
Even I fell for such a low trick.

248
00:20:48,230 --> 00:20:49,860
Look, these exam questions are five years old.

249
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:59,140
I told you they were unreliable.

250
00:20:59,360 --> 00:21:01,340
Yange Hall has stood in Lugong Town for centuries,

251
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:03,490
yet nobody knows Mr. Yan's true background.

252
00:21:03,710 --> 00:21:05,420
How dare you buy exam questions from him?

253
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:10,250
What a crafty old thing.

254
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:14,450
I need to bring up a big shot

255
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:17,250
to make him give out all the questions.

256
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:24,420
Just some gifts, please accept them.

257
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,290
These are predicted two-choice test questions sorted

258
00:21:30,710 --> 00:21:32,580
from past records.

259
00:21:33,070 --> 00:21:34,180
Your Highness, here you are.

260
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:39,690
I'll open this for you.

261
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:48,770
No...

262
00:21:52,510 --> 00:21:53,730
This is way too much!

263
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:56,580
It covers astrology, divination

264
00:21:57,030 --> 00:21:58,940
and cultivation arts from every school.

265
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:01,730
If you master all of this,

266
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:03,690
I'm sure you'll pass the trials.

267
00:22:11,710 --> 00:22:13,010
This isn't just food.

268
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:15,660
It's pure silver! Such extravagance.

269
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:18,140
This suits me perfectly.

270
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,420
Where's Lei Xiuyuan?

271
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:21,770
Why isn't he with you?

272
00:22:22,510 --> 00:22:23,180
He...

273
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:25,010
he is staying right where

274
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:26,140
he ought to be.

275
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:37,420
Flower Fairy, where are you?

276
00:22:37,440 --> 00:22:38,900
Flower Fairy, where are you?

277
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,120
[Miaoqing]

278
00:22:45,230 --> 00:22:47,580
Flower Fairy? Demon Lord?

279
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:55,730
Records of Immortals and Demons in the Sea of Illusory Love?

280
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:08,380
Save me!

281
00:23:14,640 --> 00:23:15,340
Xiaobangchui!

282
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:23,940
Help me!

283
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:28,490
Get me out of here!

284
00:23:29,920 --> 00:23:31,450
This place is pretty nice.

285
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:33,450
Stay here, or you'll bring me troubles.

286
00:23:33,880 --> 00:23:35,860
If you don't save me, I'll never let go.

287
00:23:36,510 --> 00:23:37,010
You!

288
00:23:40,230 --> 00:23:40,660
Let go of me!

289
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,860
Your Highness.

290
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,900
Help me!

291
00:23:44,550 --> 00:23:46,180
Please! Your Highness!

292
00:23:46,470 --> 00:23:47,100
Leave her be.

293
00:23:48,230 --> 00:23:48,770
Let go!

294
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:52,620
Watch out!

295
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:11,730
These assassins can't see a thing.

296
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:13,660
Your Highness, run!

297
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,970
They've come to kill you!

298
00:24:25,790 --> 00:24:26,420
Stop them!

299
00:24:37,550 --> 00:24:38,250
Let me go!

300
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:24,530
Who dares stir up trouble here?

301
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:32,690
Where are they?

302
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:43,730
Thank you for saving us

303
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:44,690
and chasing the killers away.

304
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:45,900
You said

305
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:48,140
they were targeting me.

306
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:51,380
It doesn't matter who they targeted.

307
00:25:51,470 --> 00:25:53,140
All thanks to Your Highness,

308
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:53,770
sheltered by heaven,

309
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,100
we've all got a share of your fortune

310
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:55,940
and made it out safe.

311
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:06,450
Is Lei Xiuyuan the one you are looking for?

312
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,420
Yes.

313
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:11,690
He's got the Gaolu clan mark.

314
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:16,580
Gaolu was destroyed long ago, and our whole clan was killed.

315
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:19,620
To let me escape,

316
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:22,860
my mom sent Lei Yuan, Mr. Lei's adopted kid,

317
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:24,730
to pretend to be me

318
00:26:25,310 --> 00:26:28,180
and lead Wugou's and the Longming Sanctuary's killers away.

319
00:26:29,230 --> 00:26:30,450
He was only eleven,

320
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:34,050
six months younger than me.

321
00:26:34,840 --> 00:26:36,010
Only Mr. Lu was with him.

322
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:39,010
We all thought he died.

323
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,210
Turns out

324
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,530
he's alive.

325
00:27:00,360 --> 00:27:01,250
Get lost.

326
00:27:05,600 --> 00:27:06,580
I want to survive

327
00:27:07,120 --> 00:27:08,100
and find Shanhua.

328
00:27:09,200 --> 00:27:10,490
So pitiful.

329
00:27:11,510 --> 00:27:13,770
But none of my business.

330
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:30,420
What? Save Lei Xiuyuan?

331
00:27:32,470 --> 00:27:34,860
Who said she'd obey every word

332
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,140
I say?

333
00:27:36,990 --> 00:27:38,900
I don't mean to refuse,

334
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,530
but this guy

335
00:27:42,840 --> 00:27:45,970
is unlucky, and I fear it will taint your luck.

336
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,420
Nonsense!

337
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,290
Tongzhou's luck

338
00:27:50,510 --> 00:27:52,010
won't be ruined by some wild guy.

339
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:55,010
No. He's a walking bad luck magnet.

340
00:27:55,510 --> 00:27:56,100
Think about it.

341
00:27:56,310 --> 00:27:58,770
He alone brought death to his entire village,

342
00:27:59,070 --> 00:28:00,050
and even crossed the Longming Sanctuary.

343
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,290
How ill-omened that is!

344
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:02,530
No need to worry about that.

345
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:03,940
Just get him out,

346
00:28:04,230 --> 00:28:06,180
and I'll let you join the trial with me.

347
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:13,100
Do I have to go rescue him?

348
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:20,290
Can't we just bribe Mr. Yan?

349
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:22,770
You think I haven't thought of that?

350
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:24,690
I tried bribing him ages ago,

351
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,970
but he wouldn't accept

352
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:27,970
whatever I offered.

353
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,730
If even you can't sway him,

354
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,730
I stand no chance at all.

355
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:38,180
[Yue Law]
The Yue Law states clearly:

356
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:43,900
Human traffickers get 300 cane blows, and two years of hard labor.

357
00:28:44,710 --> 00:28:46,010
Lugong Town is part of the Yue State, so…

358
00:28:46,990 --> 00:28:48,250
Since Your Highness wants him,

359
00:28:48,270 --> 00:28:50,100
I'll bring him back safe and sound.

360
00:28:59,230 --> 00:29:00,210
Hold your needle!

361
00:29:02,790 --> 00:29:03,820
Mr. Yan!

362
00:29:04,510 --> 00:29:05,050
Oh, no.

363
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:07,860
Even if he is being stubborn,

364
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:08,770
you can discipline him,

365
00:29:08,790 --> 00:29:09,820
but he doesn't deserve death.

366
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:12,690
There is a Longming Sanctuary's toxic mark on his nape.

367
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,660
I meant to cure him with the golden needle.

368
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:15,820
But you burst in,

369
00:29:17,070 --> 00:29:18,210
and the needle struck the Fengchi acupoint.

370
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:22,490
Now he's paralyzed in the face.

371
00:29:23,270 --> 00:29:24,860
He can't speak properly today.

372
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:30,450
It's all a misunderstanding.

373
00:29:31,270 --> 00:29:31,970
Misunderstanding?

374
00:29:33,030 --> 00:29:34,180
You may use the front door,

375
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,620
yet flew in through the window.

376
00:29:37,470 --> 00:29:38,660
To tell you the truth,

377
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:41,420
I came here specially to visit you.

378
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:45,730
Oh? Want to sell yourself to my hall too?

379
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:50,730
About the unfinished opera from yesterday,

380
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:53,690
I came to ask how it ends.

381
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:58,100
You know Records of Immortals and Demons in the Sea of Illusory Love?

382
00:29:58,840 --> 00:30:00,660
Sure, I've read over twenty versions.

383
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,860
Which version do you like best?

384
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:06,860
The one marked Yan.

385
00:30:07,470 --> 00:30:10,730
It states the Flower Fairy giggles, turns around,

386
00:30:10,990 --> 00:30:11,940
lifts her skirt,

387
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:14,490
and kicks the Demon Lord straight off the Immortal Execution Platform.

388
00:30:14,510 --> 00:30:16,450
So satisfying, utterly stirring!

389
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,140
A kindred spirit!

390
00:30:24,120 --> 00:30:25,100
Let's talk inside.

391
00:30:25,470 --> 00:30:25,970
Alright.

392
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:30,490
Make tea for our guest.

393
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:32,290
Don't sit there like a log!

394
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:35,730
Brew the finest tea.

395
00:30:37,840 --> 00:30:38,940
This way, please.

396
00:30:41,070 --> 00:30:42,770
Why not stay here and partner up with me?

397
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:46,140
Let me tell you, with great stories in hand,

398
00:30:46,360 --> 00:30:47,900
we can dominate all realms.

399
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:48,770
Sounds great!

400
00:30:49,550 --> 00:30:51,580
But I have to take the academy exam

401
00:30:51,990 --> 00:30:53,940
and find my family.

402
00:30:55,230 --> 00:30:55,730
You…

403
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:05,530
What's wrong with you? So clumsy!

404
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:06,620
Can't even serve tea properly.

405
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,290
What? Want to beat me?

406
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,050
Look.

407
00:31:12,160 --> 00:31:12,900
Mr. Yan,

408
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:14,620
I run my business

409
00:31:14,710 --> 00:31:15,530
by one rule:

410
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:17,010
top quality, fair prices, honest to both young and old.

411
00:31:17,470 --> 00:31:18,530
He is far from qualified.

412
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:21,290
Look. I'll take him back to train properly

413
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,380
and bring him back to you, alright?

414
00:31:23,710 --> 00:31:24,140
Let's go.

415
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:28,250
Don't bother over such trivial matters.

416
00:31:28,550 --> 00:31:29,820
I'll train him myself.

417
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:32,140
Think about it.

418
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,580
You're swamped with work and still writing stories

419
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:35,860
for us fans.

420
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:38,210
How could I let you waste time on this?

421
00:31:38,790 --> 00:31:39,970
I'm taking him away now. Come on.

422
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:41,530
Stop.

423
00:31:48,710 --> 00:31:51,730
Xiaobangchui, that's not fair play.

424
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,770
I bought him with my money.

425
00:31:54,550 --> 00:31:56,340
You can't just take him away as you please.

426
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,490
I'll pay you back the food cost.

427
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:01,620
No need.

428
00:32:02,470 --> 00:32:05,250
Rare goods once sold, no refunds.

429
00:32:08,990 --> 00:32:10,490
I'm taking him away no matter what.

430
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:14,380
Go!

431
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:21,970
You can't take him away.

432
00:32:36,920 --> 00:32:38,580
You're not going anywhere today.

433
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:39,660
You!

434
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:49,860
Run!

435
00:32:59,270 --> 00:33:00,180
I'm returning him unharmed.

436
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:07,730
The trial's starting. Get over there.

437
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:10,050
You helped me?

438
00:33:11,880 --> 00:33:13,660
No problem. Let's take the trial together.

439
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:18,050
That's great to have Your Highness with us.

440
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:23,970
If you ever harm me again,

441
00:33:24,230 --> 00:33:26,380
I'll skin, dismember and sell you by weight.

442
00:33:29,990 --> 00:33:31,180
Your Highness has magic treasures,

443
00:33:31,840 --> 00:33:33,100
Lei Xiuyuan has spirit power,

444
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:35,100
and I've got wits.

445
00:33:35,230 --> 00:33:36,860
We will be unbeatable.

446
00:33:39,030 --> 00:33:40,490
Let's go now.

447
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:45,290
Only by slaying the host can I force the fox spirit out.

448
00:33:46,790 --> 00:33:47,490
Move.

449
00:33:54,030 --> 00:33:55,100
It's time.

450
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:58,580
You have 24 hours from now.

451
00:33:58,840 --> 00:34:00,180
Make it out of this valley

452
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:03,380
before noon tomorrow,

453
00:34:08,630 --> 00:34:11,700
and you'll pass the second trial.

454
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:29,610
The trial begins.

455
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,450
What are you doing here? Get away!

456
00:34:59,470 --> 00:35:00,010
Let's go.

457
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:20,780
Your Highness!

458
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,700
Your Highness!

459
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:26,090
Anyone here?

460
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:34,010
Tongzhou, are you still mad at me?

461
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:40,090
Tongzhou,

462
00:35:40,550 --> 00:35:41,450
Xiaobangchui

463
00:35:41,470 --> 00:35:43,050
isn't on our side at all.

464
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:45,300
I was afraid she'd slow us down.

465
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,300
Still, you shouldn't be so reckless.

466
00:35:48,150 --> 00:35:49,170
If you do this again,

467
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:50,220
I'll send you back.

468
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:52,700
Alright. I won't do it next time.

469
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:54,090
Don't send me away.

470
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:00,610
Anyone here? Make a sound!

471
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,970
Oh, no. I lost my powerful ally.

472
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,610
It's freezing cold.

473
00:36:11,110 --> 00:36:11,970
Why is it so frigid?

474
00:36:11,990 --> 00:36:14,090
We must get out of here soon,

475
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:14,860
or else…

476
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:31,780
Bless me.

477
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:38,300
This will work.

478
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,700
The ancient Zhurong Stone.

479
00:37:59,990 --> 00:38:02,940
Xuanshanzi really splurged a fortune on this.

480
00:38:25,470 --> 00:38:26,780
Tongzhou, you're amazing!

481
00:38:29,720 --> 00:38:30,420
Let's go.

482
00:38:31,990 --> 00:38:34,970
Never thought someone so young

483
00:38:35,670 --> 00:38:37,300
could wield an ancient spirit treasure.

484
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:40,650
Truly an extraordinary talent.

485
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:43,380
He is using Xingzheng Hall's supreme treasure,

486
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:46,700
so he's got a huge edge over other examinees.

487
00:38:47,590 --> 00:38:50,220
- Li, that's not right. - Stop arguing.

488
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,220
Let's check the others.

489
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,490
There may be someone stronger.

490
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:07,970
No way,

491
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,490
not this again.

492
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:34,200
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

493
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:37,120
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

494
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:40,880
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

495
00:39:41,630 --> 00:39:42,490
It's you.

496
00:39:42,490 --> 00:39:43,160
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

497
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:44,970
Where's His Highness?

498
00:39:46,800 --> 00:39:47,570
How should I know?

499
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:53,090
Stay alive. I'm retreating.

500
00:40:02,960 --> 00:40:05,300
Bro... jump with me!

501
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:28,490
All limbs intact, thank heavens I had a cushion.

502
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:35,780
Can't attack openly, or the academy will find out.

503
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,170
Lost your wits?

504
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:47,860
It'd be easier if he really lost his wits.

505
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:54,050
Say something. Are you alright?

506
00:40:54,470 --> 00:40:55,010
Speak to me.

507
00:40:57,630 --> 00:40:58,490
You're actually fine.

508
00:41:07,630 --> 00:41:08,170
Are you

509
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:10,820
cold?

510
00:41:12,470 --> 00:41:14,130
Obviously, snow and ice are everywhere.

511
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:15,090
Of course, I'm cold.

512
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:21,970
What? Trying to trick me again?

513
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:23,530
Don't move.

514
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,650
Why's my whole body warming up?

515
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:07,450
You're channeling your spirit power to me?

516
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:13,170
No wonder I took a fancy to you, Metal Spirit Root.

517
00:42:13,400 --> 00:42:16,010
Putting others first, so kind and righteous.

518
00:42:16,670 --> 00:42:18,570
Those examinees are quite hopeful.

519
00:42:18,800 --> 00:42:19,740
Two more trials left.

520
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:27,420
If I kill her now,

521
00:42:27,990 --> 00:42:29,610
the fox spirit may reveal itself to save her.

522
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:33,740
Now's the chance to shatter her meridians.

523
00:42:38,160 --> 00:42:40,760
[The Eternal Fragrance]
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

524
00:42:52,800 --> 00:42:55,740
♪It's me, blinded by longing♪

525
00:42:55,900 --> 00:42:58,700
♪Every glance lands on you♪

526
00:42:58,860 --> 00:43:03,980
♪Fire and water clash, yet we cling inseparably♪

527
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:07,260
♪Lotus broken, threads still bind us♪

528
00:43:07,580 --> 00:43:10,580
♪My heart calm till you stir storms and rain♪

529
00:43:11,220 --> 00:43:14,500
♪You are my destined rival♪

530
00:43:15,660 --> 00:43:20,620
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes, fate ties me to you♪

531
00:43:21,420 --> 00:43:26,740
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas, I follow no one but you♪

532
00:43:27,300 --> 00:43:33,260
♪Bitterness brews sweet bliss, drained in one sip♪

533
00:43:33,700 --> 00:43:39,020
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

534
00:43:39,140 --> 00:43:44,740
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks; you complete my five elements♪

535
00:43:44,820 --> 00:43:50,420
♪Burning love, unbridled hatred, they suit each other well♪

536
00:43:50,580 --> 00:43:56,620
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

537
00:43:57,060 --> 00:44:05,580
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust, stay side by side till the end♪

538
00:44:14,820 --> 00:44:17,540
♪Sometimes I throw petty fits♪

539
00:44:17,820 --> 00:44:20,580
♪I blame all troubles on you♪

540
00:44:20,780 --> 00:44:25,900
♪Though distant on the surface, our souls resonate as one♪

541
00:44:26,340 --> 00:44:29,220
♪We wander far, parted to separate corners♪

542
00:44:29,500 --> 00:44:32,460
♪Yet my heart still leans toward you, my foe♪

543
00:44:33,140 --> 00:44:36,420
♪I sigh and laugh, defeated in this game of affection♪

544
00:44:37,660 --> 00:44:42,620
♪Winters pass, springs come; bound for lifetimes, fate ties me to you♪

545
00:44:43,340 --> 00:44:48,660
♪Mountains, rivers, lakes and seas, I follow no one but you♪

546
00:44:49,220 --> 00:44:55,180
♪Perhaps endless tangling is our silent bond♪

547
00:44:55,620 --> 00:45:00,940
♪Love and feud balance out, I'm yours alone♪

548
00:45:01,060 --> 00:45:06,660
♪Fated foes, fate plays tricks; you complete my five elements♪

549
00:45:06,740 --> 00:45:12,340
♪Burning love, unbridled hatred, they suit each other well♪

550
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:18,580
♪If you don't leave, I'll never abandon you♪

551
00:45:19,180 --> 00:45:28,380
♪We'll dwell in mortal dust, stay side by side till the end♪
